OverHistory.UPDCommentry: Romario Shepherd to Ayush Badoni, WICKET Ayush Badoni run out Nicholas Pooran (Lucknow Super Giants 169 Runs for 7 wickets). Good length, outside off stump, Ayush skips down the track and slashes at this, fails to get bat on ball and Holder is off for the bye, Pooran is quick to throw the ball to the bowler and Shepherd effects a run out at the non-striker's end. Lucknow Super Giants end their innings on 169/7. Stay tuned for the chase!
